de.topicmapslab.tmql4j.components.processor.results
Interface IResult

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Object>
All Known Implementing Classes:
CTMFragment, OntopiaResult, Result, SimpleResult, WrappedOntopiaResult, XMLFragment
public interface IResult
extends java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Object>

Interface definition of a tuple of the generated result set. The result represents a row in the result set and contains a number of atomic or complex values like Topics, Associations, CTM- or XTM-strings.

Author:
Sven Krosse
